    {
      "heading": "题解",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>理解题意</strong>",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>直观</strong>：很显然，我们只需要在意 $k$ 的奇偶性即可。为偶，本题就是裸的<strong>最大子段和问题</strong>；为奇，Alice 能拿一个 <code>b[i]</code>，需要进行考虑。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>深层</strong>：<strong>最大子段和问题</strong>可以想到使用<strong>前缀和</strong>，然后维护一个<strong>最小前缀和</strong>与<strong>当前枚举的前缀和</strong>相减算答案。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "但是你维护了<strong>最小前缀和</strong>，不代表能拿到<strong>最大的 b</strong>，两者一起维护难度很大。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>正难则反</strong>，我们<strong>换一个参数枚举</strong>，考虑枚举 <code>b[i]</code>。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "要想 <code>b[i]</code> 所在区间的和最大，维护<strong>最小前缀前缀和</strong> <code>mnpre[i - 1]</code> 与<strong>最大后缀前缀和</strong> <code>mxsuf[i]</code> 即可。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "<strong>难点</strong>",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "发现枚举前缀和不对劲后，<strong>正难则反</strong>，果断枚举 $b[i]$。",
          "depth": 2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "代码",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "void solve(int CASE)\n{\n\tll n, k; cin >> n >> k;\n\tvar a = vector<ll>(n + 1);\n\tvar b = vector<ll>(n + 1);\n\tfa(i, 1, n)cin >> a[i];\n\tfa(i, 1, n)cin >> b[i];\n\tif (k % 2 == 0) {\n\t\tll dp = a[1], ans = a[1];\n\t\tfa(i, 2, n) {\n\t\t\tdp = max(a[i], dp + a[i]);\n\t\t\tans = max(ans, dp);\n\t\t}\n\t\tcout << ans << endl;\n\t\treturn;\n\t}\n\n\tll ans = a[1] + b[1], mxb = b[1];\n\tvar pre = vector<ll>(n + 1);\n\tpre[1] = a[1];\n\tll mnpre = min(-b[1], a[1]);\n\n\tfa(i, 2, n) {\n\t\tpre[i] = pre[i - 1] + a[i];\n\t\tif (b[i] > mxb) {\n\t\t\tmnpre += mxb;\n\t\t\tmxb = b[i];\n\t\t\tmnpre -= mxb;\n\t\t}\n\t\tans = max(ans, pre[i] - mnpre);\n\t\tmnpre = min(mnpre, pre[i]);\n\t}\n\tcout << ans << endl;\n\treturn;\n}",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
